seventy-seven bronze <i>yokai.</i>

00:21:09.853 --> 00:21:12.313 position:50% align:center
Spread out over the
800 meters of this street,

00:21:12.397 --> 00:21:15.108 position:50% align:center
which leads directly
to Sakaiminato Station.

00:21:15.191 --> 00:21:18.194 position:50% align:center
[ASAI] Almost 200?
That's pretty amazing!

00:21:18.278 --> 00:21:20.071 position:50% align:center
Check it out! What's this?

00:21:20.155 --> 00:21:22.198 position:50% align:center
It looks like a dragon to me.

00:21:22.282 --> 00:21:25.702 position:50% align:center
Let's see... It's not!
It's a <i>shiro-uneri</i> !

00:21:25.785 --> 00:21:27.954 position:50% align:center
Shiro. What now?

00:21:28.038 --> 00:21:30.206 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Okay, next! What's this?

00:21:30.290 --> 00:21:31.416 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
A crayfish?

00:21:31.499 --> 00:21:33.960 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Err! An <i>amikiri</i> !

00:21:34.044 --> 00:21:36.212 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
These are tough. What's next?

00:21:36.296 --> 00:21:37.881 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
This, right here!

00:21:37.964 --> 00:21:38.715 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
A yeti!

00:21:38.798 --> 00:21:40.133 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
<i>Keukegen</i> !

00:21:40.216 --> 00:21:42.886 position:50% align:center
What's this "yeti" stuff?
That's not even Japanese.

00:21:42.969 --> 00:21:44.512 position:50% align:center
[screams]

00:21:44.596 --> 00:21:46.848 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Dammit. You try this next one.

00:21:46.931 --> 00:21:49.392 position:50% align:center
Here. Wait, this is--

00:21:49.476 --> 00:21:51.311 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
<i>Rokuro-Kubi</i> ! It's <i>Rokuro-Kubi</i> !

00:21:51.394 --> 00:21:52.896 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
I knew that one!

00:21:52.979 --> 00:21:55.106 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI screaming]

00:21:55.190 --> 00:21:57.192 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Okay, moving on!

00:22:00.528 --> 00:22:01.821 position:50% align:center
[ASAI]
Yep, this is the place.

00:22:01.905 --> 00:22:05.241 position:50% align:center
[SAKAKI] The Mizuki Shigeru
Museum is a must-see.

00:22:06.242 --> 00:22:07.869 position:50% align:center
[SAKAKI, ASAI gasp]

00:23:46.509 --> 00:23:49.137 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Hey. There's my name for once.